import React from 'react'
import { Container } from '../../GlobalStyles'
import { SignInForm, Title, Input, SignUpLink, ConnectButton, InputWrapper, IconContainer, Text, SignUpContainer } from './SignIn.elements'
import {FaUserAlt} from 'react-icons/fa'
import {BsLockFill} from 'react-icons/bs'

const SignIn = () => {
  return (
    <>
    <Container>
      <SignInForm>
        <Title>Se connecter</Title>
        <InputWrapper>
            <IconContainer>
                <FaUserAlt style={{width:'25px', height:'25px'}}/>
            </IconContainer>
            <Input placeholder='Email' type='email'/>
        </InputWrapper>
        <InputWrapper>
            <IconContainer>
                <BsLockFill style={{width:'25px', height:'25px'}}/>
            </IconContainer>
            <Input placeholder='Mot de passe' type='password'/>
        </InputWrapper>
        <SignUpContainer>
            <Text>Vous n'etes pas encore menmbre ?</Text>
            <SignUpLink> Rejoignez-nous</SignUpLink>
        </SignUpContainer>
        <ConnectButton>Se connecter</ConnectButton>
      </SignInForm>
    </Container>
    </>
  )
}

export default SignIn
